Class CrmTags

java.lang.Object
net.tangly.erp.crm.domain.CrmTags
public final class CrmTags extends Object
A taxonomy of tags for a customer relationship management system. The namespace is naturally crm. Additional namespaces were added to introduce standard tags such as location tags.
